<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 18:11:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>斯塔默总理当选后，以色列罕见延长驻英国大使任期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/in-rare-move-israel-to-extend-term-of-ambassador-to-u-k-following-election-of-pm-starmer/00000191-56d2-d79a-a3f5-ded20fd30000</link><description>以色列外交部正在寻求延长齐皮·霍托夫利 (Tzipi Hotovley) 以色列驻英国大使的任期，理由是她拥有“广泛的关系网络”以及推进以色列“战略利益”的能力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/in-rare-move-israel-to-extend-term-of-ambassador-to-u-k-following-election-of-pm-starmer/00000191-56d2-d79a-a3f5-ded20fd30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 314 天：哈马斯称，自战争开始以来，至少有 40,000 名加沙人被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-314-at-least-40-000-gazans-killed-since-war-began-hamas-says/00000191-5687-d623-a1f3-76d7bdf70000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达卡塔尔，与哈马斯就停火/人质释放协议进行谈判 ■ 白宫：情报显示“伊朗尚未放弃攻击以色列的威胁” ■ 据报道，拜登的中东高级特使表示“需要做什么”黎巴嫩将缓和以色列和真主党之间的紧张局势，并“不破坏调解人为确保停战所做的努力” ■ 这是战争开始 314 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-314-at-least-40-000-gazans-killed-since-war-began-hamas-says/00000191-5687-d623-a1f3-76d7bdf70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前首席拉比批评本格维尔访问圣殿山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-former-chief-rabbi-criticizes-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-5699-db91-a7dd-779981600000</link><description>约瑟夫拉比说：“我们都相信一位上帝，希望各国之间实现和平，我们不能让极端的边缘人士引导我们。”其他主要拉比也谴责周一的访问。</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:18:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-former-chief-rabbi-criticizes-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-5699-db91-a7dd-779981600000</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示多哈峰会已经开始，会谈将持续到周五</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-doha-summit-has-started-talks-to-continue-into-friday/00000191-56c1-d79a-a3f5-ded373250000</link><description>以色列和哈马斯周四在卡塔尔重启停火和释放人质协议的谈判</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 16:07:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-doha-summit-has-started-talks-to-continue-into-friday/00000191-56c1-d79a-a3f5-ded373250000</guid></item><item><title>40,000 个关于已不复存在的加沙的提醒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/40-000-reasons-for-thought-testimony-to-the-lives-in-gaza-that-are-no-more/00000191-5656-d623-a1f3-76d781790000</link><description>这里的每个点都象征着一个人、他们的希望和对生活的渴望——尽管如此。加沙战争使他们变得匿名，每个人都只剩下另一个数字</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 15:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/40-000-reasons-for-thought-testimony-to-the-lives-in-gaza-that-are-no-more/00000191-5656-d623-a1f3-76d781790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列希望捕获伊朗的“幽灵舰队”，这些油轮在雷达下为其轴心提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-to-trap-irans-ghost-fleet-oil-tankers-financing-its-axis-under-the-radar/00000191-5669-d61e-a7b1-f7ff52800000</link><description>《国土报》调查发现，伊朗油轮由世界各地的稻草公司注册，并关闭应答器以隐藏其运营</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 15:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-wants-to-trap-irans-ghost-fleet-oil-tankers-financing-its-axis-under-the-radar/00000191-5669-d61e-a7b1-f7ff52800000</guid></item><item><title>袭击以色列高级官员的伊朗黑客现在将目标瞄准特朗普和哈里斯竞选团队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/iranian-hackers-that-hit-top-israelis-officials-now-targeting-trump-harris-campaigns/00000191-55ba-d2c7-a9bf-7dbb8eaa0000</link><description>在特朗普竞选团队确认罗杰·斯通的电子邮件帐户可能遭到黑客攻击后，谷歌研究人员表示，专门针对以色列备受瞩目的政治和安全目标进行网络间谍活动的伊朗组织也瞄准了美国总统竞选活动</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:27:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/iranian-hackers-that-hit-top-israelis-officials-now-targeting-trump-harris-campaigns/00000191-55ba-d2c7-a9bf-7dbb8eaa0000</guid></item><item><title>“记住我们的名字”：由于害怕被遗忘，年轻的加沙人在临终前记录了最后的遗嘱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/remember-our-names-fearing-oblivion-young-gazans-recorded-last-wills-before-dying/00000191-4b2b-dfee-a3f3-5feb9a300000</link><description>一位从未离开家的足球运动员、一位想要提高政治意识的经济学家以及一位即使在死后仍继续提供内容的电影制片人。自战争开始以来，他们是加沙地带 4 万人遇难的人之一。除了死亡之外，许多人还担心自己会成为“一个数字”，并采取措施确保他们不会被遗忘</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/remember-our-names-fearing-oblivion-young-gazans-recorded-last-wills-before-dying/00000191-4b2b-dfee-a3f3-5feb9a300000</guid></item><item><title>由辛贝特和摩萨德领导人率领的以色列团队抵达多哈参加加沙停火峰会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/led-by-shin-bet-and-mossad-chiefs-israeli-team-heads-to-doha-for-gaza-cease-fire-summit/00000191-5231-d984-a5ff-f2f713580000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦高级官员告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡和某些内阁成员的言论表明谈判不太可能取得进展，其成功取决于美国的压力</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 12:29:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/led-by-shin-bet-and-mossad-chiefs-israeli-team-heads-to-doha-for-gaza-cease-fire-summit/00000191-5231-d984-a5ff-f2f713580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列航空公司在加沙战争的帮助下季度利润创纪录的 1.47 亿美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airline-el-al-rakes-in-record-147m-in-quarterly-profits-with-help-of-gaza-war/00000191-552a-d5d7-adbb-757a65c80000</link><description>得益于在以色列运营的外国航空公司的竞争减少，该公司在本世纪初面临着严重的财务困境，但今年第二季度自 2022 年底以来的净财务债务减少了 10.89 亿美元</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airline-el-al-rakes-in-record-147m-in-quarterly-profits-with-help-of-gaza-war/00000191-552a-d5d7-adbb-757a65c80000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯卫生部称，自战争开始以来，加沙死亡人数已超过4万</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-surpasses-40-000-since-war-began-hamas-health-ministry-says/00000191-4c06-d695-a7b5-de0f450a0000</link><description>据哈马斯管理的卫生部称，约 70% 的伤亡者是妇女和儿童，约 17,000 名儿童失去了父母之一或双亲。 ■ 加沙的卫生系统处于崩溃边缘，约 12,000 名伤者需要紧急疏散接受治疗国外</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:08:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/gaza-death-toll-surpasses-40-000-since-war-began-hamas-health-ministry-says/00000191-4c06-d695-a7b5-de0f450a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室要求甘茨偿还美国正式访问费用19,000美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-demands-gantz-pay-back-19-000-for-official-u-s-visit/00000191-54d4-d5d7-adbb-74f406340000</link><description>以色列议员本尼·甘茨（Benny Gantz）还是内塔尼亚胡战时内阁成员时进行的三月访问包括与副总统哈里斯和其他官员的会面。项目办称甘茨无权进行此次访问</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 07:40:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-demands-gantz-pay-back-19-000-for-official-u-s-visit/00000191-54d4-d5d7-adbb-74f406340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列掌握着释放人质的关键 - 但伊朗将决定中东是否爆发战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-holds-the-key-to-freeing-the-hostages-but-iran-decides-if-the-region-goes-to-war/00000191-52b5-dc60-a397-57f5b6310000</link><description>周四的多哈峰会就像一个俄罗斯娃娃，充满了层层障碍：目前还不清楚内塔尼亚胡给了以色列谈判代表多大的灵活性，以及​​这对哈马斯来说是否足够；没有人知道伊朗和真主党是否会以加沙停火为借口，放弃对两起耻辱性暗杀事件的军事反应</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 03:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-holds-the-key-to-freeing-the-hostages-but-iran-decides-if-the-region-goes-to-war/00000191-52b5-dc60-a397-57f5b6310000</guid></item><item><title>美国在加沙峰会前加大压力 - 并计划在失败后改变策略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steps-up-the-pressure-ahead-of-gaza-summit-and-plans-a-change-of-tactics-if-it-fails/00000191-521f-dc13-ab99-db1f4aa10000</link><description>拜登政府可能会向以色列和哈马斯提出一个不可谈判的、是或否的主张。如果内塔尼亚胡拒绝，华盛顿可能会将失败归咎于他，并可能对其政府内的极右翼采取进一步行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/u-s-steps-up-the-pressure-ahead-of-gaza-summit-and-plans-a-change-of-tactics-if-it-fails/00000191-521f-dc13-ab99-db1f4aa10000</guid></item><item><title>法国和英国外长将访问以色列，以缓和紧张局势，防止战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article-live/senior-palestinian-official-israeli-comments-suggest-doha-talks-unlikely-to-end-in-deal/00000191-53ce-d6a2-a7dd-d3dea0fb0000</link><description>以色列代表团抵达卡塔尔进行停火、释放人质谈判 ■ 数百人聚集在特拉维夫，呼吁达成协议释放人质 ■ 法国、英国外交部长将于周五在耶路撒冷会见以色列外长 ■ 火箭弹袭击后以色列北部爆发火灾来自黎巴嫩 ■ 美国制裁胡塞武装、真主党附属个人和公司</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-15/ty-article-live/senior-palestinian-official-israeli-comments-suggest-doha-talks-unlikely-to-end-in-deal/00000191-53ce-d6a2-a7dd-d3dea0fb0000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学校长因加沙抗议政策和反犹太主义批评而辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/columbia-university-president-resigns-amid-criticism-of-gaza-protests-policy-antisemitism/00000191-5377-d39d-a79f-f77f174a0000</link><description>米努什·沙菲克 (Minouche Shafik) 的领导层面临严格审查，鉴于她对抗议活动处理不当以及校园反犹太主义的指控，要求她辞职的呼声越来越高</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 00:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-15/ty-article/.premium/columbia-university-president-resigns-amid-criticism-of-gaza-protests-policy-antisemitism/00000191-5377-d39d-a79f-f77f174a0000</guid></item><item><title>如果从以色列国防部长到伊朗的所有人都希望加沙停火，这并不是投降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-14/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-capitulation-if-everyone-from-iran-to-israels-defense-chiefs-wants-a-cease-fire/00000191-51ab-ddb5-affd-5bffb82a0000</link><description>本周，以色列国防部长、以色列公众、美国、英国和德国大使以及伊朗政府似乎达成了罕见的共识</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 17:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-14/ty-article/.highlight/its-not-capitulation-if-everyone-from-iran-to-israels-defense-chiefs-wants-a-cease-fire/00000191-51ab-ddb5-affd-5bffb82a0000</guid></item><item><title>为了避免对隔离公共祈祷的强烈反对，特拉维夫没有让任何人满意</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-bid-to-avoid-backlash-over-segregated-public-prayer-tel-aviv-leaves-no-one-satisfied/00000191-5042-d94f-adf1-d06e22ac0000</link><description>去年特拉维夫反对使用公共空间进行性别隔离祈祷的抗议活动引发了全国性的辩论，之后该市对这种做法进行了取缔。但围绕以色列世俗首都性质的争论仍在上演，一些人警告“这将以另一场爆炸告终”</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 17:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-bid-to-avoid-backlash-over-segregated-public-prayer-tel-aviv-leaves-no-one-satisfied/00000191-5042-d94f-adf1-d06e22ac0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔阻止阿拉伯军官指挥希伯伦边境警察，转而推挤犹太军官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-blocks-arab-officers-posting-to-command-border-police-in-hebron/00000191-518b-da93-add3-db8bcf6a0000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔试图任命一名极端正统犹太教军官，而不是一名阿拉伯基督教军官，来指挥包括闪点族长墓在内的地区，该部长经常在那里祈祷</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-blocks-arab-officers-posting-to-command-border-police-in-hebron/00000191-518b-da93-add3-db8bcf6a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 313 天：以色列高级拉比谴责本格维尔访问圣殿山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-313-senior-israeli-rabbis-condemn-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-51a7-d211-a7fd-fbe7344b0001</link><description>美国总统拜登的中东事务高级特使在贝鲁特会见黎巴嫩议会议长后表示，“我们仍然相信，没有人真正希望黎巴嫩和以色列之间爆发全面战争” ■ 美国、英国和德国驻以色列特使公开呼吁立即接受加沙停火/人质释放协议 ■ 战争开始 313 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:14:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-313-senior-israeli-rabbis-condemn-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-visit/00000191-51a7-d211-a7fd-fbe7344b0001</guid></item></channel></rss>